		<title>狗狗的忌妒心超重？牠以為自己生日　真相曝光瞬間一秒翻臉 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/09/22/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e7%9a%84%e5%bf%8c%e5%a6%92%e5%bf%83%e8%b6%85%e9%87%8d%ef%bc%9f%e7%89%a0%e4%bb%a5%e7%82%ba%e8%87%aa%e5%b7%b1%e7%94%9f%e6%97%a5%e3%80%80%e7%9c%9f%e7%9b%b8%e6%9b%9d%e5%85%89%e7%9e%ac/</link>
		
